<node CREATED="1566553220801" ID="ID_1388450769" MODIFIED="1566553220801" TEXT="Seven Basic Principles of Software Engineering Barry W. Boehm TRW Defense Systems Group This paper attempts to distill the large number of individual aphorisms on good software engineering into a small set of basic principles. Seven principles have been determined which form a reasonably independent and complete set. These are: (1)" />
