<node CREATED="1566553220812" ID="ID_1833080527" MODIFIED="1566553220812" TEXT="Learn how to improve the quality of your code by programming alongside another person. This course will teach you the proper techniques and many benefits of pair programming how to set up your workspace and how to pair-program remotely." />
