<node CREATED="1566553220812" ID="ID_110815696" MODIFIED="1566553220812" TEXT="Pair programming is the practice of pairing up to work on programming tasks. Usually most people imagine two developers seated at the same computer sharing the keyboard. But with the increasing popularity of remote coding platforms it&#226;&#8364;&#8482;s now possible to pair program thousands of miles apart." />
