<node CREATED="1566553220812" ID="ID_1602334576" MODIFIED="1566553220812" TEXT="One more pair programming pattern frequently employed by developers is the ping pong pairing. In this approach the driver drafts a test for behavior and requests the reviewer to apply the behavior." />
