<node CREATED="1566553220812" ID="ID_626684111" MODIFIED="1566553220812" TEXT="What is pair-programming? Pair-programming is a technique in Agile Software Development where two engineers share a single workstation. In this technique one engineer is the driver  whom has control of the mouse and keyboard to write the code while the other serves as the navigator  reviewing the code that the other is writing while " />
