<node CREATED="1566553220814" ID="ID_1026263533" MODIFIED="1566553220814" TEXT="Kanban is enormously prominent among todays agile software teams but the kanban methodology of work dates back more than 50 years. In the late 1940s Toyota began optimizing its engineering processes based on the same model that supermarkets were using to stock their shelves." />
